    {
      "type": 12,
      "content": {
        "version": "NotebookGroup/1.0",
        "groupType": "editable",
        "items": [
          {
            "type": 1,
            "content": {
              "json": "## Por Tipo de Recurso — Quais serviços mais consomem Private Endpoints?\n\nEsta visualização agrupa todos os Private Endpoints pelo tipo de recurso Azure ao qual se conectam, ajudando a identificar quais serviços são os maiores consumidores.\n\n> **Abordagem drill-down:** Selecione um Tipo de Recurso abaixo para visualizar os Private Endpoints individuais. Isso evita limites de consulta do ARG quando o tenant possui milhares de PEs."
            },
            "name": "ByResourceTypeDescription"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "resources\r\n| where type =~ 'microsoft.network/privateendpoints'\r\n| mv-expand connection = properties.privateLinkServiceConnections\r\n| extend targetResourceId = tostring(connection.properties.privateLinkServiceId)\r\n| extend targetResourceType = extract(@'/providers/([^/]+/[^/]+)', 1, targetResourceId)\r\n| summarize PECount = count() by targetResourceType\r\n| order by PECount desc",
              "size": 0,
              "showAnalytics": true,
              "title": "Private Endpoints por Tipo de Recurso de Destino",
              "showExportToExcel": true,
              "queryType": 1,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.resourcegraph/resources",
              "crossComponentResources": [
                "{Subscriptions}"
              ],
              "visualization": "barchart",
              "chartSettings": {
                "xAxis": "targetResourceType",
                "yAxis": [
                  "PECount"
                ],
                "showLegend": true
              }
            },
            "name": "ResourceTypeChart"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "resources\r\n| where type =~ 'microsoft.network/privateendpoints'\r\n| mv-expand connection = properties.privateLinkServiceConnections\r\n| extend targetResourceId = tostring(connection.properties.privateLinkServiceId)\r\n| extend targetResourceType = extract(@'/providers/([^/]+/[^/]+)', 1, targetResourceId)\r\n| extend subnetId = tostring(properties.subnet.id)\r\n| parse kind=regex subnetId with '/subscriptions/' peSubId '/resourceGroups/' peRG '/providers/Microsoft.Network/virtualNetworks/' vnetName '/subnets/' subnetName\r\n| extend vnetId = strcat('/subscriptions/', peSubId, '/resourceGroups/', peRG, '/providers/Microsoft.Network/virtualNetworks/', vnetName)\r\n| summarize PECount = count(), VNETs = dcount(vnetId), Subnets = dcount(strcat(vnetId, '/', subnetName)), Subscriptions = dcount(peSubId) by targetResourceType\r\n| order by PECount desc",
              "size": 0,
              "showAnalytics": true,
              "title": "Resumo por Tipo de Recurso (clique em uma linha para filtrar os detalhes abaixo)",
              "showExportToExcel": true,
              "queryType": 1,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.resourcegraph/resources",
              "crossComponentResources": [
                "{Subscriptions}"
              ],
              "visualization": "table",
              "gridSettings": {
                "formatters": [
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "PECount",
                    "formatter": 4,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "palette": "blue"
                    }
                  }
                ],
                "filter": true,
                "labelSettings": [
                  {
                    "columnId": "targetResourceType",
                    "label": "Tipo de Recurso"
                  },
                  {
                    "columnId": "PECount",
                    "label": "Qtd. de PEs"
                  },
                  {
                    "columnId": "VNETs",
                    "label": "VNETs Distintas"
                  },
                  {
                    "columnId": "Subnets",
                    "label": "Sub-redes Distintas"
                  },
                  {
                    "columnId": "Subscriptions",
                    "label": "Assinaturas Distintas"
                  }
                ]
              },
              "exportFieldName": "targetResourceType",
              "exportParameterName": "SelectedResourceType"
            },
            "name": "ResourceTypeSummaryGrid"
          },
          {
            "type": 1,
            "content": {
              "json": "---\n### Detalhes para: {SelectedResourceType}\n\n> Exibindo até 1.000 resultados. Use **Exportar para Excel** ou o botão **Abrir no ARG** para o conjunto completo de dados."
            },
            "conditionalVisibility": {
              "parameterName": "SelectedResourceType",
              "comparison": "isNotEqualTo",
              "value": ""
            },
            "name": "ResourceTypeDetailHeader"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "resources\r\n| where type =~ 'microsoft.network/privateendpoints'\r\n| mv-expand connection = properties.privateLinkServiceConnections\r\n| extend targetResourceId = tostring(connection.properties.privateLinkServiceId)\r\n| extend targetResourceType = extract(@'/providers/([^/]+/[^/]+)', 1, targetResourceId)\r\n| where targetResourceType =~ '{SelectedResourceType}'\r\n| extend targetResourceName = extract(@'/([^/]+)$', 1, targetResourceId)\r\n| extend subnetId = tostring(properties.subnet.id)\r\n| parse kind=regex subnetId with '/subscriptions/' peSubId '/resourceGroups/' peRG '/providers/Microsoft.Network/virtualNetworks/' vnetName '/subnets/' subnetName\r\n| project PEName = name, targetResourceName, vnetName, subnetName, resourceGroup, subscriptionId, targetResourceId, id\r\n| order by vnetName asc, PEName asc",
              "size": 0,
              "showAnalytics": true,
              "title": "Private Endpoints — {SelectedResourceType}",
              "showExportToExcel": true,
              "queryType": 1,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.resourcegraph/resources",
              "crossComponentResources": [
                "{Subscriptions}"
              ],
              "gridSettings": {
                "formatters": [
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "targetResourceId",
                    "formatter": 13,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "linkTarget": "Resource",
                      "showIcon": true
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "id",
                    "formatter": 13,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "linkTarget": "Resource",
                      "showIcon": true
                    }
                  }
                ],
                "rowLimit": 1000,
                "filter": true,
                "hierarchySettings": {
                  "treeType": 1,
                  "groupBy": [
                    "vnetName"
                  ],
                  "expandTopLevel": false
                },
                "labelSettings": [
                  {
                    "columnId": "PEName",
                    "label": "Nome do PE"
                  },
                  {
                    "columnId": "targetResourceName",
                    "label": "Recurso de Destino"
                  },
                  {
                    "columnId": "vnetName",
                    "label": "VNET"
                  },
                  {
                    "columnId": "subnetName",
                    "label": "Sub-rede"
                  },
                  {
                    "columnId": "resourceGroup",
                    "label": "Grupo de Recursos do PE"
                  },
                  {
                    "columnId": "subscriptionId",
                    "label": "Assinatura"
                  },
                  {
                    "columnId": "targetResourceId",
                    "label": "Link do Recurso de Destino"
                  },
                  {
                    "columnId": "id",
                    "label": "Link do Recurso PE"
                  }
                ]
              }
            },
            "conditionalVisibility": {
              "parameterName": "SelectedResourceType",
              "comparison": "isNotEqualTo",
              "value": ""
            },
            "name": "ResourceTypeDetailGrid"
          }
        ]
      },
      "conditionalVisibility": {
        "parameterName": "selectedTab",
        "comparison": "isEqualTo",
        "value": "byresourcetype"
      },
      "name": "ByResourceTypeGroup"
    },
    {
      "type": 12,
      "content": {
        "version": "NotebookGroup/1.0",
        "groupType": "editable",
        "items": [
          {
            "type": 1,
            "content": {
              "json": "## Por Assinatura — Distribuição de Private Endpoints\n\nEsta visualização mostra o uso de PEs agregado por assinatura, ajudando a identificar quais assinaturas possuem a maior densidade de PEs. O limite por assinatura é de **64.000**."
            },
            "name": "BySubscriptionDescription"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "resources\r\n| where type =~ 'microsoft.network/privateendpoints'\r\n| summarize PECount = count() by subscriptionId\r\n| join kind=leftouter (\r\n    resourcecontainers\r\n    | where type =~ 'microsoft.resources/subscriptions'\r\n    | project subscriptionId, SubName = name\r\n) on subscriptionId\r\n| extend PctOfLimit = round(todouble(PECount) / 64000.0 * 100, 2)\r\n| project SubName, subscriptionId, PECount, PctOfLimit, Remaining = 64000 - PECount\r\n| order by PECount desc",
              "size": 0,
              "showAnalytics": true,
              "title": "Private Endpoints por Assinatura (Limite: 64.000)",
              "showExportToExcel": true,
              "queryType": 1,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.resourcegraph/resources",
              "crossComponentResources": [
                "{Subscriptions}"
              ],
              "gridSettings": {
                "formatters": [
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "PECount",
                    "formatter": 8,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "min": 0,
                      "palette": "blue"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "PctOfLimit",
                    "formatter": 3,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "min": 0,
                      "max": 100,
                      "palette": "greenRed"
                    },
                    "numberFormat": {
                      "unit": 1,
                      "options": {
                        "style": "decimal",
                        "maximumFractionDigits": 2
                      }
                    }
                  }
                ],
                "filter": true,
                "labelSettings": [
                  {
                    "columnId": "SubName",
                    "label": "Nome da Assinatura"
                  },
                  {
                    "columnId": "subscriptionId",
                    "label": "ID da Assinatura"
                  },
                  {
                    "columnId": "PECount",
                    "label": "Qtd. de PEs"
                  },
                  {
                    "columnId": "PctOfLimit",
                    "label": "% do Limite de 64K"
                  },
                  {
                    "columnId": "Remaining",
                    "label": "Restante"
                  }
                ]
              }
            },
            "name": "BySubscriptionGrid"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "resources\r\n| where type =~ 'microsoft.network/privateendpoints'\r\n| extend subnetId = tostring(properties.subnet.id)\r\n| parse kind=regex subnetId with '/subscriptions/' peSubId '/resourceGroups/' peRG '/providers/Microsoft.Network/virtualNetworks/' vnetName '/subnets/' subnetName\r\n| summarize PECount = count() by subscriptionId, vnetName\r\n| join kind=leftouter (\r\n    resourcecontainers\r\n    | where type =~ 'microsoft.resources/subscriptions'\r\n    | project subscriptionId, SubName = name\r\n) on subscriptionId\r\n| project SubName, vnetName, PECount\r\n| order by SubName asc, PECount desc",
              "size": 0,
              "showAnalytics": true,
              "title": "Qtd. de PEs por Assinatura e VNET",
              "showExportToExcel": true,
              "queryType": 1,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.resourcegraph/resources",
              "crossComponentResources": [
                "{Subscriptions}"
              ],
              "gridSettings": {
                "formatters": [
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "PECount",
                    "formatter": 8,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "min": 0,
                      "palette": "blue"
                    }
                  }
                ],
                "filter": true,
                "hierarchySettings": {
                  "treeType": 1,
                  "groupBy": [
                    "SubName"
                  ],
                  "expandTopLevel": true
                },
                "labelSettings": [
                  {
                    "columnId": "SubName",
                    "label": "Assinatura"
                  },
                  {
                    "columnId": "vnetName",
                    "label": "VNET"
                  },
                  {
                    "columnId": "PECount",
                    "label": "Qtd. de PEs"
                  }
                ]
              }
            },
            "name": "BySubscriptionVnetGrid"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "resources\r\n| where type =~ 'microsoft.network/privateendpoints'\r\n| summarize PECount = count() by subscriptionId\r\n| join kind=leftouter (\r\n    resourcecontainers\r\n    | where type =~ 'microsoft.resources/subscriptions'\r\n    | project subscriptionId, SubName = name\r\n) on subscriptionId\r\n| project SubName, PECount\r\n| order by PECount desc",
              "size": 1,
              "title": "Distribuição de PEs entre Assinaturas",
              "queryType": 1,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.resourcegraph/resources",
              "crossComponentResources": [
                "{Subscriptions}"
              ],
              "visualization": "piechart"
            },
            "name": "BySubscriptionPie"
          }
        ]
      },
      "conditionalVisibility": {
        "parameterName": "selectedTab",
        "comparison": "isEqualTo",
        "value": "bysubscription"
      },
      "name": "BySubscriptionGroup"
    }
  ],
  "$schema": "https://github.com/Microsoft/Application-Insights-Workbooks/blob/master/schema/workbook.json",
  "fallbackResourceIds": [
    "Azure Monitor"
  ]
}